    <item>
      <title>杜德利：中国需要谨慎对待关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-04/china-needs-to-tread-carefully-with-tariffs-dudley-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富兰克林邓普顿公共市场高级投资策略师卡特里娜·杜德利表示，特朗普总统并没有虚张声势地征收关税，中国这次的处境不同，需要谨慎行事。她在《未平仓合约》节目中与彭博社的凯蒂·格雷菲尔德和罗曼·博斯蒂克进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-04/china-needs-to-tread-carefully-with-tariffs-dudley-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 21:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 创下史上最长连胜纪录，市值增至 2400 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/meta-adds-235-billion-of-value-in-longest-winning-streak-ever</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者对这家社交媒体巨头的人工智能战略表示欢迎，Meta Platforms Inc. 的股价周二连续第 12 个交易日上涨，这是该公司有史以来最长的上涨势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/meta-adds-235-billion-of-value-in-longest-winning-streak-ever</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 16:05:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税忧虑和美国经济走强导致美元下跌预期短暂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/dollar-drop-seen-brief-amid-tariff-worries-us-economic-strength</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们押注，鉴于美国经济相对强劲以及贸易战可能迫使投资者进入避险资产的背景，周二美元的暴跌可能是短暂的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/dollar-drop-seen-brief-amid-tariff-worries-us-economic-strength</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 16:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
