      <title>特朗普暂停贸易关税给新兴市场带来喘息机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-s-trade-tariffs-pause-offers-breather-to-emerging-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们对特朗普总统的威胁可能引发全面贸易战的担忧有所缓解，新兴市场股票和货币周二出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-s-trade-tariffs-pause-offers-breather-to-emerging-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 11:20:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
